skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: irvine mud line
des:
Get the latest status of park openings and closures for Irvine, CA.

Ask for the status of a park to see if it is open or closed, as well as when the last update was made and any additional notes.

You can also say List Parks to get the list of parks that the skill has information on.

Field Designation: Baseball/Softball fields are numbers (1, 2, 3, etc.). Soccer/Lacrosse/Football fields are letters (A, B, C, etc.)

Park information provided by City of Irvine.
For more details, see http://www.cityofirvine.org/athletics-sports/field-conditions
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
